## SSH Access

You have SSH keys mounted at `/home/node/.ssh/`. Use them to:
- Run diagnostic commands on ocean: `ssh ocean.home <command>`
- Check service status: `ssh ocean.home systemctl status <service>`
- View logs: `ssh ocean.home journalctl -u <service> --since '10 min ago'`
- Test ansible changes: `ssh ocean.home ansible-playbook --check ...`

